1. reload .vimrc

:source ~/.vimrc

2. 设置

:set list?   获取当前设置的值
:set list!   取反值
:set nolist
:set list
:set listchars?
:set number
:set nonu
:set relativenumber

:set nohls
:set nohlsearch

:function

3. tabs vs spaces

:retab convert tabs to spaces

https://howchoo.com/g/m2u0nthkyti/vim-convert-tabs-to-spaces

https://github.com/tpope/vim-sleuth

:e  :edit
:so :source

:call <TAB>
:!
:sh
:edit! it will discard local changes and reload

:!git diff %
:!git add %

:source %
:source $MYVIMRC
% means the current open buffer


4. vim --clean . start vim with no plugins, no viminfo

5. Map Ctrl + p to open fuzzy find (FZF)
nnoremap <c-p> :Files<cr>

https://devhints.io/vimscript
https://github.com/thoughtbot/dotfiles
